SUMMARY:Senior 50+ Housing Fair
DTSTAMP:20260325T064009Z
DTSTART:20260401T003000Z
DESCRIPTION:Meet representatives from Renton-based senior housing communiti
	es\, referral specialists\, and related agencies such as housing repair se
	rvices. Open House format\; pre-registration is strongly encouraged. Age 5
	0 & Up Pre-register at rentonwa.gov/register Course \\# 28684\n\nhttps://s
	eatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/senior-50-housing-fair/18252305/2026-
	03-31T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All Events
